link: WHO Coronavirus disease (COVID-2019) situation reports

dat <- 
  "data/dat_cofdeath.csv" %>% 
  read.csv(stringsAsFactors = F)

g <-
  dat %>% 
  ggplot()+
  aes(Confirmed, Death, color = Area)+
  geom_point()+
  geom_path()+
  geom_text(data = dat %>% 
              group_by(Area) %>% 
              filter(Death == max(Death) & 
                       Confirmed == max(Confirmed)),
            aes(label = Area, x = Confirmed + 20),
            hjust = 0)+
#  scale_x_continuous(limits = c(0, 3000))+
  theme_bw()+
  theme(legend.position = "none")
g

g_jp_G <-
  dat %>%
  filter(Area %in% c("Japan", "Germany")) %>% 
  ggplot()+
  aes(Confirmed, Death, color = Area)+
  geom_point()+
  geom_path()+
  geom_text(data = dat %>% 
              filter(Area %in% c("Japan", "Germany")) %>% 
              group_by(Area) %>% 
              filter(Death == max(Death) & 
                       Confirmed == max(Confirmed)),
            aes(label = Area, x = Confirmed + 20),
            hjust = 0)+
  scale_x_continuous(limits = c(0, 6500))+
  theme_bw()+
  theme(legend.position = "none")

g_jp_G

g + 
  facet_wrap(~Area)

dat_week <-
  dat %>% 
  mutate(Date = ymd(Date)) %>% 
  arrange(desc(Date)) %>% 
  group_by(Area) %>% 
  mutate(tag = if_else(Date == max(Date), 0, 1),
         tag = cumsum(tag) %% 7)

dat_week %>% 
  ggplot()+
  aes(Confirmed, Death, color = Area)+
  geom_point()+
  geom_path()+
  geom_text(data = dat %>% 
              group_by(Area) %>% 
              filter(Death == max(Death) & 
                       Confirmed == max(Confirmed)),
            aes(label = Area, x = Confirmed + 20),
            hjust = 0)+
  geom_vline(data = dat_week %>% filter(tag == 0),
             aes(xintercept = Confirmed), linetype = "dotted")+
#  scale_x_continuous(limits = c(0, 3000))+
  theme_bw()+
  theme(legend.position = "none")+
  facet_wrap(~Area)

dat_week %>% 
  filter(Area %in% c("Japan", "Germany")) %>% 
  ggplot()+
  aes(Confirmed, Death, color = Area)+
  geom_point()+
  geom_path()+
  geom_text(data = dat %>% 
              filter(Area %in% c("Japan", "Germany")) %>%
              group_by(Area) %>% 
              filter(Death == max(Death) & 
                       Confirmed == max(Confirmed)),
            aes(label = Area, x = Confirmed + 20),
            hjust = 0)+
  geom_vline(data = dat_week %>%
               filter(tag == 0) %>%
               filter(Area %in% c("Japan", "Germany")),
             aes(xintercept = Confirmed), linetype = "dotted")+
#  scale_x_continuous(limits = c(0, 3000))+
  theme_bw()+
  theme(legend.position = "none")+
  facet_wrap(~Area, scales = "free_x")

dat %>% 
  filter(Area == "Germany") %>% 
  filter(Death >= 2) %>% 
  lm(Death ~ Confirmed, data = .) %>% 
  summary()
